# Page Structure Requirements

## 1. Essential Pages Only
- **Home/Dashboard**: Main application interface
- **Login**: User authentication
- **User Management**: User administration (if applicable)
- **Settings**: Application configuration (if applicable)

## 2. Page Layout
```tsx
// Standard Page Layout
<div className="min-h-screen bg-background">
  <Header />
  <div className="flex">
    <Sidebar />
    <main className="flex-1 p-6">
      <PageHeader />
      <Content />
    </main>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</div>
```

## 3. Navigation Structure
```tsx
// Navigation Menu
<nav className="space-y-2">
  <NavItem href="/dashboard" icon={Home}>
    Dashboard
  </NavItem>
  <NavItem href="/users" icon={Users}>
    Users
  </NavItem>
  <NavItem href="/settings" icon={Settings}>
    Settings
  </NavItem>
</nav>
```
